Package UI

Class UpperCard

java.lang.Object
UI.UpperCard
public class UpperCard extends Object
Represents the upper card panel in the UI, handling the configuration of various components like Text, Image, and Table. This class provides a user interface for selecting these components and configuring their respective properties.
